A\sin(x+θ)=D
(E,F),(G,H)
A\sin(E+θ)=F,  A\sin(G+θ)=H
A\sin(E)\cos(θ)+A\cos(E)\sin(θ)=F, A\sin(G)\cos(θ)+A\cos(G)\sin(θ)=H
X=A\cos(θ),  Y=A\sin(θ)
X\sin(E)+Y\cos(E)=F,  X\sin(G)+Y\cos(G)=H
